JOSEPH FOX, GEORGE ASHBRIDGE, JAMES WRIGHT, SAMUEL RHOADS, JAMES WEBB, Eſquires, of the Aſſembly, and ſeveral Magiſtrates, and a Number of Gentlemen from Philadelphia, and other Parts of the Province.


