                        A Liſt of the Northern INDIANS, including Men, Women, and Children, at the Treaty at Lancaſter, Auguſt 1762.

Oneidas, 156.

Onondagoes, 156.

Tuſcaroras, 156.

Nanticokes, 156.

Conoys, 156.

Senecas, — 97.

Cayugas, and 128.

Saponys, and a Mixture of 128.

Shawaneſe and Munſeys, 128.

TEEDYUSCUNG, and the Delawares with him, 176. In all, 557.

